gov.usgs.anss.seed

Class SEEDChannel

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.usgs.anss.seed.SEEDChannel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable

    public class SEEDChannel
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable
    SEEDChannel.java This class represent (basically) a Blockette 52 SEED blockette and an epoch following same. That is it contains information needed to build one of these. It is used (originally) by the InvToSEED.java to store/organize the channels as the Inventory Trees are parsed with response information Created on March 3, 2005, 1:23 PM
